.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "April 2024" "C - Simple Shell Project"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple shell implementation in UNIX

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simple_shell
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]... [\fICOMMAND\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The simple_shell is a basic shell program written in C as part of C - Simple Shell Group Project. It provides a simple command-line interface and executes them accordingly.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -h, --help
Display help information

.SH USAGE
To start the simple shell, run below command in your terminal:

.BR simple_shell

.SH EXAMPLE
.PP
Run a simple command:
.nf
.B simple_shell pwd
.fi

